reviewText: acquire the skill and artistry you desire! many studios use these videos to "show how is it is done...."  you can get that skill first hand!

More low to high intermediate West Coast swing. Covers roll turns, whips, hammerlocks, wraps, over wraps, spins, and turns. I recommend this series, which seems to have little feedback at Amazon. My background is three years of private/group lessons, plus dancing at the Tucson Swing Club. I find reviewing this series very helpful as a review of West Coast Swing patterns.

One of the best West Coast Swing DVD on the market. I am still watching it to learn patterns and moves. January 11, 2012.
